files.name: .goreleaser.yml
files.content:
before:
  hooks:
    - go mod tidy

builds:
  - main: .
    env:
      - CGO_ENABLED=0
    goos:
      - windows
    goarch:
      - amd64

    ignore:
      - goos: windows
        goarch: 'arm64'

    binary: 'wxapkg'

    flags:
      - '-trimpath'
    ldflags:
      - '-s -w'
      - '-X main.version={{ .Version }}'
      - '-X main.commit={{ .ShortCommit }}'
    hooks:
      post: "upx --lzma {{ .Path }}"

changelog:
  filters:
    exclude:
      - '^doc:'
      - typo
      - (?i)foo
      - '^ref'
      - '^style'
  groups:
    - title: Features
      regexp: "^.*feat[(\\w)]*:+.*$"
      order: 0
    - title: 'Bug fixes'
      regexp: "^.*fix[(\\w)]*:+.*$"
      order: 1
    - title: Others
      order: 999

archives:
  - format: binary

checksum:
  algorithm: md5
